[heard] nQoYJ_00004.mp3: you are all competing for the attention of the most influential guests a senior geisha might subtly steer a wealthy patron away from you a rival from another house might accidentally spill tea on your priceless kimono a disaster that could add months to your debt gossip is a weapon wielded with the precision of a sword a whispered rumor about your character true or not could ruin your reputation you learn to be wary to trust no one completely not even the girls you share a roof with the world of flowers and willows the karayukai is beautiful but it has thorns the ultimate goal for a geisha is not marriage it's to find adana adana is a wealthy patron who agrees to cover all of your expenses your kimonos your lessons your living costs all of it this is not a simple transaction adana is not a client for a single night it is a long-term complex relationship almost like a marriage but without the legal contract he becomes your protector and benefactor in return you offer him your loyalty and companionship he has exclusive rights to your time and your art finding adana is the only real path to financial security and high status in the geisha world attracting a potential donna is the most subtle art of all it's not done with overt flirting it is done through conversation through proving your intelligence and your grace you make him feel seen and understood
